@HostAddress = http://localhost:5252

## Minimal API - Enum value casing

### Route enum parameter - exact casing (expect 200)
GET {{HostAddress}}/hello/Active/world
Accept: application/json

###

### Route enum parameter - lowercase (expect 400)
GET {{HostAddress}}/hello/active/world
Accept: application/json

###

### Route enum parameter - uppercase (expect 400)
GET {{HostAddress}}/hello/ACTIVE/world
Accept: application/json

###

### Route enum parameter - non-enum segments case-insensitive (expect 200)
GET {{HostAddress}}/HELLO/Active/WORLD
Accept: application/json

###

### Query enum parameter - exact casing
GET {{HostAddress}}/query?status=Active
Accept: application/json

###

### Query enum parameter - lowercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/query?status=active
Accept: application/json

###

### Query enum parameter - uppercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/query?status=ACTIVE
Accept: application/json

###

### Header enum parameter - exact casing
GET {{HostAddress}}/header
X-Status: Active
Accept: application/json

###

### Header enum parameter - lowercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/header
X-Status: active
Accept: application/json

###

### Header enum parameter - uppercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/header
X-Status: ACTIVE
Accept: application/json

###

### Form enum parameter - exact casing
POST {{HostAddress}}/form
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

status=Active

###

### Form enum parameter - lowercase
POST {{HostAddress}}/form
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

status=active

###

### Form enum parameter - uppercase
POST {{HostAddress}}/form
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

status=ACTIVE

###

### JSON body - exact casing
POST {{HostAddress}}/body
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "test", "status": "Active"}

###

### JSON body - lowercase
POST {{HostAddress}}/body
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "test", "status": "active"}

###

### JSON body - uppercase
POST {{HostAddress}}/body
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "test", "status": "ACTIVE"}

###

### JSON body - numeric value
POST {{HostAddress}}/body
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "test", "status": 1}

###

## Controller-based API - Enum value casing

### Controller route parameter - exact casing (expect 200)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/Active/details
Accept: application/json

###

### Controller route parameter - lowercase (expect 200 - case-insensitive)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/active/details
Accept: application/json

###

### Controller route parameter - uppercase (expect 200 - case-insensitive)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/ACTIVE/details
Accept: application/json

###

