GET {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/query?status=Active
Accept: application/json

###

### Controller query parameter - lowercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/query?status=active
Accept: application/json

###

### Controller query parameter - uppercase
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/query?status=ACTIVE
Accept: application/json

###

