POST {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/form
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

status=Active

###

### Controller form parameter - lowercase
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/enum/form
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

status=active

